name: Catwalk Model and Stars Fashionable Animals
name_original: Catwalk Model and Stars Fashionable Animals
description:
Show off your fancy supermodel finesse by walking up and down the catwalk. But, uh oh! Your supermodel rivals have left their exotic pets around the catwalk. Avoid them or your career will come to an unglamourous end.

To play:

  • Tap screen to start
  • Tap the back foot to walk forward.

Made with images from www.openclipart.com

Created using Pocket Code for Android.

To run:

  • Download & install Pocket Code app
  • Download the game file and install in the Pocket Code directory on device.
